Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.64,0:00:21.44,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找尋著看不見的明天 著急地用手觸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.60,0:00:25.95,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.10,0:00:38.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是沒有出口的迷宮 就像需要解謎的拼圖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.20,0:00:49.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有奇跡出現  夢想也將成為勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  圍繞的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.13,0:00:57.91,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.42,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  因為那份思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:03.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給了我無形的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:09.70,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像稍微感受到了迷惘和煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.70,0:01:11.33,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.48,0:01:14.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  圍繞的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.49,0:01:23.63,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  對你的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.67,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.63,0:21:42.93,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在心中綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.09,0:21:49.77,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中燃盡  僅是一束火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.02,0:21:58.41,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滿是隔閡的街上 如遊戲般的迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.54,0:22:02.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小丑的心情躊躇著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.53,0:22:11.07,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要踐踏悲傷的殘片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.15,0:22:15.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.96,0:22:23.52,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解開今晚的謎底仍然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.80,0:22:28.04,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.35,0:22:35.57,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is passion　兩個人的手中充滿的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.73,0:22:42.53,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入黑暗之中   想緊緊擁抱住陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.95,0:22:48.06,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在迷宮中相互Kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.20,0:22:57.09,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁向樂園  僅差一道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.45,0:00:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時代的演進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.85,0:00:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困難的案件也與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.85,0:00:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的關鍵在於揭穿不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.05,0:00:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅是利用而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.56,0:00:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.06,0:00:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.36,0:00:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.37,0:01:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅鬼村火祭殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿笠博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.15,0:01:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候才能找到那些黑衣男子的線索啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.05,0:01:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓毛利叔叔成為名偵探之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.56,0:01:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來還以為委託他辦的案子增加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.06,0:01:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫傢伙的情報就比較容易到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.26,0:01:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的案子增加了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.56,0:01:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加是增加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.87,0:02:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那幫傢伙的消息一點也沒弄到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.37,0:02:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情急不來的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.37,0:02:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是輕舉妄動的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.97,0:02:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定反而被他們知道你的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.88,0:02:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真那樣子的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.14,0:02:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.85,0:02:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭和叔叔就會有危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.85,0:02:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有耐心等待了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.75,0:02:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待也是一名偵探必須具備的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.76,0:02:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.76,0:02:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼實驗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.56,0:02:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎 這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.07,0:02:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你應該知道這是什麼實驗了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.47,0:02:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少知道這是個危險的實驗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.35,0:02:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.05,0:02:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然碰上這種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.06,0:02:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.56,0:03:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個應該合您的意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.87,0:03:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.07,0:03:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您留下送貨的地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.87,0:03:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在工作 工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.25,0:03:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是正在跟蹤那個人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.85,0:03:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被他發現了怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.05,0:03:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子快給我回家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便跟小蘭說一聲我要晚一點回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.76,0:03:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用等我吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.77,0:03:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子不會搞砸了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.15,0:04:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是輕鬆的工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.15,0:04:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視那個男的三天就有五十萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到真的有這麼容易的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.86,0:04:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這表示社會上已有越來越多的人認定爸爸是名偵探了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.77,0:04:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我也覺得有點不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.67,0:04:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都把棘手的案子解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.17,0:04:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次把案子解決的人都是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.37,0:04:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從柯南來了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.14,0:04:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的工作好像越來越順利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.55,0:05:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是柯南把好運帶給了我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.35,0:05:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼還要在這兒待多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.76,0:05:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成他父母現在還在住院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.26,0:05:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我到阿笠博士那裡去問他的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...雖然已經出院了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.87,0:05:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他們又突然被調到國外去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天才剛剛搭飛機走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 放著柯南不管啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說到了那邊穩定下來以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.05,0:05:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會立刻和你們聯絡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.45,0:05:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他還要厚著臉皮寄住在這兒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是柯南很可憐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒有地方可去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.46,0:05:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們現在這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等於是把他拋棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.46,0:05:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著你多嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到他父母聯絡我們的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.06,0:05:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要向他們要食宿費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上八點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.57,0:05:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在遊客聚集的群馬縣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.87,0:05:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅鬼村火祭的高臺中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.37,0:06:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現一具燒焦的男性屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.14,0:06:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從死者的遺物判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名死者叫做根岸正樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年四十二歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方認為他殺的可能性很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前把案件列為兇殺案來處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確就是這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.75,0:06:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.76,0:06:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.26,0:06:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.86,0:06:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這三天我都在這個男的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.46,0:06:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說這三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.67,0:06:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.17,0:06:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天還在跟蹤這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.77,0:06:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫根岸正樹的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸好慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.55,0:06:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是去錄口供嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫叔叔跟那個叫根岸的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.55,0:06:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到昨天為止都一直在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對警方來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.96,0:06:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也沒有比他更重要的證人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼樣的事件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.26,0:06:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔你快點把整件事告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快等不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.07,0:07:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五...五億元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.37,0:07:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 在他死之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.64,0:07:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他買了價值五億元的人壽保險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.94,0:07:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是太奇怪了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.35,0:07:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份巨額人壽保險的受益人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.15,0:07:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是跟他只是朋友關係的你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.45,0:07:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿部豐先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.95,0:07:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.66,0:07:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是這件案子發生之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.56,0:07:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委託我跟蹤根岸的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.06,0:07:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會是保險金的受益人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是一場遊戲而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.37,0:07:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.43,0:07:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.47,0:07:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和根岸從大學時代至今 已經相識二十多年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.17,0:07:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天我們喝酒的時候他對我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今年都四十二歲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.84,0:07:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經不年輕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.24,0:07:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要來賭賭看我們兩個到底誰壽命比較長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.35,0:07:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒挺有意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.55,0:07:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於賭金嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.55,0:07:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五億元怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就這樣子答應他的提議了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.86,0:08:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們就為對方投保了五億元保險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.26,0:08:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 萬萬沒有想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在短短三個月裏就決出勝負了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.87,0:08:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你為什麼要請毛利來跟蹤他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.97,0:08:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也不是什麼大不了的理由啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.64,0:08:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 他找我商量說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像成為某人的目標了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.75,0:08:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕很快就會被殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.55,0:08:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被...被殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.85,0:08:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為他在跟我開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.35,0:08:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他的神色的確不太正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了以防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.56,0:08:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請毛利先生幫忙調查了三天的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.56,0:08:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.76,0:08:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.36,0:08:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事要做不能留在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.17,0:08:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹也是一家小公司的老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情很多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.97,0:08:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個殺死根岸的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.24,0:08:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們一定要快點把他找出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.34,0:08:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要找到的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.75,0:08:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會跟你說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就衷心期待囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手除了阿部豐以外沒有其他人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.36,0:09:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他又有不在場的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是完美的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.27,0:09:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可疑了 實在太可疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.97,0:09:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人肯定就是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十萬耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.24,0:09:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過跟蹤他三天就有五十萬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼講這個酬勞也太高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.45,0:09:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他那副自信滿滿的態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越想越可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那警方為什麼不把他抓起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.95,0:09:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有完美的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.25,0:09:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.86,0:09:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證明他當時不在現場的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.36,0:09:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.26,0:09:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體被發現的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.76,0:09:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是舉行火祭的星期天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.47,0:09:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前一直到星期六深夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都一直跟著死者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.24,0:09:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶案是從星期六的深夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.04,0:10:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到火祭的高臺被點上火的星期天傍晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.25,0:10:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.65,0:10:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那爸爸你懷疑的這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.35,0:10:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天肯定在紅鬼村附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.86,0:10:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.76,0:10:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從星期六早晨到星期一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.76,0:10:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是到今天白天這段時間都在外面旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.76,0:10:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們的公司組織的員工旅行 在九州
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.27,0:10:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼會覺得他有嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.47,0:10:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 我作為一名偵探的直覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在場證明嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.55,0:10:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.35,0:10:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.56,0:10:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿部這個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.96,0:10:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經把根岸的保險金都提走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.66,0:10:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.76,0:10:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢用這種方法搶走五億
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.16,0:10:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要盡全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.17,0:10:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來破解他的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.37,0:10:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.87,0:10:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是阿部到九州旅行的行程表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有紀念照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.44,0:11:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我請求目暮警部特別借給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.94,0:11:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想線索肯定就在這些照片裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.05,0:11:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會把他的破綻給找出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.65,0:11:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸正在燃燒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不要燒光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.96,0:11:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他真要作案的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.66,0:11:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在國內旅行要往返也很容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.06,0:11:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.77,0:11:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的不在場證明找不出漏洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.57,0:11:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是在凶案發生的這段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六晚上到星期日傍晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的不在場證明很完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.04,0:11:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六晚上他和員工打通宵麻將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.75,0:11:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天白天坐車在市內觀光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.65,0:11:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為證據的照片也都有保留下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.55,0:11:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他獨處的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.45,0:11:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有星期天中午前小睡的兩個小時而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.26,0:11:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他如果要在這段時間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.86,0:11:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在發現屍體的群馬縣和九州之間來回是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.37,0:12:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些照片好奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.37,0:12:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.44,0:12:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.84,0:12:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人怎麼每次都和時鐘一起拍照啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.84,0:12:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.45,0:12:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人一定非常喜歡時鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.45,0:12:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太不自然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.85,0:12:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就像是為了證明他的清白才拍的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼說的一點都沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.96,0:12:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況以前好像也發生過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推理不下去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.46,0:12:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼的話總能成為提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.37,0:12:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個袋子是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.74,0:12:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.64,0:12:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟蹤他的時候拍的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 弄亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.04,0:12:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是我為那個死者拍下的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.05,0:12:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖...痛痛統統飛掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.16,0:12:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子就是小孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.37,0:13:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.87,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次被殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的就是這個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體不是都被燒焦了麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕對錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.34,0:13:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為當時在發現屍體的火祭高臺旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.04,0:13:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了被害人的駕照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.15,0:13:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齒模也與屍體吻合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.55,0:13:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.85,0:13:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.85,0:13:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常兇手會盡可能隱瞞犯罪事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.86,0:13:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他卻把這個死者放在火祭用的高臺裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還故意在旁邊留下證實死者身份的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些行為都太反常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.17,0:13:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是屍體被發現後唯一能夠獲利的只有一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.17,0:13:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是根岸的保險受益人阿部豐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就是那個阿部豐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他有完美的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.15,0:13:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.65,0:13:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以破解他的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.15,0:14:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.55,0:14:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得我所看到的根岸先生確實是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是習慣用右手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.72,0:14:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.83,0:14:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.63,0:14:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是星期四和星期五拍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是星期六拍的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.34,0:14:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利叔叔跟蹤被殺的根岸正樹的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是星期四到星期六這三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.25,0:14:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是屍體被發現的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻是星期天的傍晚 也就是說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.32,0:14:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶案應該是在從星期六晚上到星期日傍晚之間發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最有嫌疑的阿部豐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.43,0:15:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從星期六早上開始一直到星期一的晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.03,0:15:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在九州那裡旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在場證明很充分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.53,0:15:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的推測正確的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不在場證明就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.54,0:15:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小鬼到底有完沒完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.94,0:15:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要一不注意你就給我搗亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.05,0:15:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要因為案子解不開就拿柯南出氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手肯定就是阿部豐錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他有殺人動機的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.42,0:15:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿部豐的公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.42,0:15:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來有三億元巨額債務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.25,0:15:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這債務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.43,0:15:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但能用根岸這五億元的保險金全部填滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.85,0:15:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.75,0:15:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還可以帶著剩下的兩億
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.93,0:15:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到國外從而避開警方的調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.45,0:15:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到國外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.65,0:15:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把公司拜託給別人管理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說他要暫時出國旅行一段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.85,0:15:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 他的出發時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.35,0:15:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是今晚九點鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.26,0:15:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九點鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩三個小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他逃到國外的話就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.05,0:15:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.05,0:16:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有逼那個傢伙自己承認了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.04,0:16:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須把叔叔他們帶到機場去才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就這麼辦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.75,0:16:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿部豐的不在場證明被破解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎 目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.95,0:16:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正在趕往機場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我需要你去那裏為我們作證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.45,0:16:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以快點來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.85,0:16:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我就在機場等你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.85,0:16:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 接著是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.45,0:16:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用叔叔的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.95,0:16:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.05,0:16:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們待會兒可不能礙手礙腳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次有什麼事都要跟來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的人真多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.15,0:16:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一下要找到警部他們可真得花功夫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.55,0:17:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿部豐他搭哪一班飛機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.05,0:17:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.75,0:17:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要開始登機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.75,0:17:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.95,0:17:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點冒險也只有引他出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.45,0:17:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的旅客請注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.55,0:17:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預定搭乘飛往西雅圖的九十九次航班的阿部豐先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.05,0:17:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位名叫根岸正樹的先生正在停車場等您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.55,0:17:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重複一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.55,0:17:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預定搭乘飛往西雅圖的九十九次航班的阿部豐先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.35,0:17:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位名叫根岸正樹的先生正在停車場等您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.15,0:17:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.25,0:17:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 警部我想知道這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼破解阿部豐的不在場證明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.65,0:17:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你說的破解了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.85,0:17:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.55,0:17:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計畫得不錯嘛 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.46,0:18:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰...是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實根岸被害的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在星期五晚上對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.23,0:18:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.63,0:18:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是你出發去旅行的前一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後第二天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.63,0:18:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你請了一個和根岸長得很像的冒牌貨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.55,0:18:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓毛利偵探跟蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡 你在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.15,0:18:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼做是為了讓大家認為根岸在週六的時候還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.95,0:18:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.85,0:18:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按照事先調查好的火祭的時間 按照你的計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.55,0:18:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他的屍體在星期日晚上被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.65,0:18:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候他的屍體早就被火燒焦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本無法確定死亡時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.25,0:18:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據毛利偵探的口供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.95,0:18:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者的死亡時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.65,0:18:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能被推斷成星期六晚上到星期日傍晚這段時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.95,0:18:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後到了星期一早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.05,0:18:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就裝作毫不知情的樣子回來上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在場證明就成立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 我說的對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.85,0:18:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小...小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.25,0:19:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那邊的刑警叔叔把實情告訴大家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.15,0:19:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就做出了這番推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.05,0:19:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你選那個人來代替根岸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.15,0:19:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是件很失策的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.95,0:19:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你能瞞騙過一般的偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是照片卻騙不了人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.15,0:19:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個假的根岸是個左撇子和真的不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去自首吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在來了很多刑警叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.44,0:19:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.84,0:19:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.85,0:19:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯把根岸正樹殺掉的人就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我阿部豐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.15,0:19:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我是不會去自首的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.25,0:19:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就要到國外享清福去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.06,0:19:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我會把叔叔剛才說的話告訴別人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.73,0:19:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣一個小鬼說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會有人相信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.33,0:19:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是叔叔你自己講的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.24,0:19:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們應該會相信了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.44,0:20:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把根岸正樹殺掉的人就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我阿部豐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.45,0:20:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在找死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.75,0:20:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你這個小鬼頭怎麼能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.65,0:20:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個就快要倒閉的公司的社長的心情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他自己笨才會被騙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.06,0:20:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了我的建議後就毫不猶豫地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.65,0:20:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替自己買了五億元保險的根岸是個大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.05,0:20:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本就不知道我會計畫殺他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.65,0:20:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.15,0:20:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你這個特地跑來送命的小鬼也是個大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.15,0:20:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己才是個大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.35,0:20:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你乖乖地向警方自首我還會饒了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我已經忍無可忍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.52,0:20:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你這個無藥可救的腦袋打清醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這...這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.05,0:21:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 把根岸正樹殺掉的人就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.75,0:21:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我阿部豐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.96,0:21:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是誰幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.35,0:23:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.15,0:23:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然利用我為他做不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.85,0:23:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太可惡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.23,0:23:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.33,0:23:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒充根岸的那個傢伙不是被找到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.13,0:23:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他也是受阿部的雇用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.34,0:23:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成天在那裡亂晃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.24,0:23:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我還是在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.25,0:23:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿部最後說的那句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.64,0:23:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼...我竟然栽在一個小鬼的手裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.75,0:23:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時在他附近的小鬼只有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.85,0:23:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.05,0:23:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.62,0:23:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝小孩子也不輕鬆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.33,0:23:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是個很棒的選手哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.54,0:23:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優勝錦旗被人割破了
